    <title>Scaling Vision-Language Pretraining with Synthetic Captions</title>
    <summary>  We present a scalable recipe for vision-language pretraining that replaces
noisy web captions with model-generated synthetic captions, improving downstream
zero-shot accuracy while reducing data requirements.  </summary>
